{"tid":2147072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【無綫失守】《娛樂新聞台》導演確診武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-08-09T04:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T04:09:29.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ebf8f7eeeed8bf4cdb0ff24ef2952aa21ce27f90","tid":2147072,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:07:52.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎在香港爆發第三波疫情，無綫電視城終於「失守」，《蘋果》收到消息，指無綫娛樂新聞台一名導演Joey於昨晚確診，據知與其同住的3名家人亦中招，令電視城人心惶惶！<br />\n<br />\n據了解娛樂新聞台約有40名台前幕後，而今次中招的導演是廠內導演，不用外景拍攝，但仍有部份被列入緊密接觸者需要進行檢測，及留在中家工作，而娛樂新聞台主播周奕瑋、許文軒、蘇可欣、陳婉衡、鄭衍峰等亦人人自危。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200809/SPWYE6Q23C3B55QC4J2IAM5L4I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200809%2FSPWYE6Q23C3B55QC4J2IAM5L4I%2F&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=7a70366c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200809%2FSPWYE6Q23C3B55QC4J2IAM5L4I%2F&h=f33a4269\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200809/SPWYE6Q23C3B55QC4J2IAM5L4I/</a>"},{"pid":"872346d48d25e55a9202ddb5020a204be7afc5fb","tid":2147072,"uid":163057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SnFpPq7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSnFpPq7.png&h=77e4cf37&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}